{"title":"母乳","authors":["叶延滨"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":3,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"母乳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶延滨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没吮汲过母乳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一想到这点就十分困惑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总想找到那只"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛装童年的奶瓶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰凉冰凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数次手的抚摸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然不能把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这只坚硬的铜炮弹壳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拭出一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乳白的温馨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲说那是我的奶瓶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当填充在炮弹里的火药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把死神送往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烽火中的碉堡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹壳这战神的铜塑像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用冷冷的眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守住我的襁褓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲说一生下我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就没有奶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，那件灰黄的军衣下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不也有丰满的胸脯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是血是能点燃的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是恨是能冒烟的恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个女战士的怀中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着一支破旧的步枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉阳造"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪是她的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也是她的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪搂在她的胸前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伏在她的背上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏在暖烘烘的背上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳朵贴紧母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听惯两种声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗心砰砰地跳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支枪砰砰地响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是老山羊的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道当老乡用怜悯的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拂母亲发丝上的尘土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一碗碗羊奶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸透我的笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小羊羔一定用委屈的眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盯住我那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糊满羊乳的脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是老黄牛的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道在野战医院的山沟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条驮着忧伤的牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干瘪的乳房淌不满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只搪瓷茶杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小牛犊一定用没角的额"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶撞着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的那个摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"士兵的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是羊的儿子牛的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是大地用草在反刍的胃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揉出的乳汁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收养的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有枪声和炮声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能够惊醒我的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在死神舞蹈歌唱的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晾上一串尿布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮乎乎的生命之诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗子弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射穿了瘪凹的军用饭盒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让乳白色的米面糊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂着另一个婴儿——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这块失血太多的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即将分娩一个新国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那布满弹孔的战旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那散着乳香的尿布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让多少感情的乳汁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淌进我的人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有吮汲过母乳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知母乳的味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这只摆了三十八年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铜弹壳里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅袅地飘出乳色的硝烟……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}